### Reg-Tech API — Transmission & Inbound Endpoints (Layer 5)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = <paste-ta-jwt-here>

### ─── Check Outbound Transmission Status ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/transmission/00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000201/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── List Inbound Transmissions ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/inbound?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Receive Inbound Package (CTS Webhook) ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/cts/inbound
Content-Type: application/json
X-CTS-Signature: sha256=abcdef1234567890

{
  "sourceJurisdiction": "DE",
  "messageRefId": "DE2024CRS-INBOUND-001",
  "packageUrl": "https://cts.oecd.org/packages/DE2024CRS-INBOUND-001.enc",
  "timestamp": "2024-12-20T14:30:00Z",
  "metadata": {
    "sendingCountry": "DE",
    "receivingCountry": "IE",
    "messageType": "CRS",
    "reportingPeriod": "2024"
  }
}

###

### ─── Process ACK for Outbound Transmission ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/cts/inbound
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "ACK",
  "originalMessageRefId": "IE2024CRS001",
  "sourceJurisdiction": "DE",
  "timestamp": "2024-12-16T09:00:00Z",
  "status": "ACCEPTED"
}

###

### ─── Process NACK for Outbound Transmission ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/cts/inbound
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "NACK",
  "originalMessageRefId": "IE2024CRS-FAIL",
  "sourceJurisdiction": "DE",
  "timestamp": "2024-12-16T09:00:00Z",
  "status": "REJECTED",
  "errors": [
    {
      "code": "CRS_ERR_001",
      "message": "Invalid MessageRefId format",
      "severity": "ERROR"
    }
  ]
}
